title: A Unique Ramadan by Shaykh Salih as-Suhaymee ( حَفِظَهُ الله)

media:group.media:title: A Unique Ramadan by Shaykh Salih as-Suhaymee ( حَفِظَهُ الله)
media:group.media:description:
A lecture delivered by the noble Shaykh on the 20th April 2020. 
It was organised by Masjid as-Sunnah in Sheffield.
Please assist and support this Masjid in order that they can continue to arrange lectures and conferences - inviting the senior and respected Scholars of this Ummah.
Translated by Abu Sulaymaan
